abbot (Amanuensis for BusyBodies on Twisted) is an XMPP bot based on Twisted
and Wokkel.

CONFIGURATION:
 1. Create a new XMPP account user@domain.com
 2. Edit abbot.tac and replace abbot@ransford.org with user@domain.com
 3. Put user@domain.com's password in a file 'password.txt' in this directory

USAGE: twistd -ny abbot.tac
  -or- twistd -y abbot.tac     # daemonize
